		<!--HK Edit Start for Touch-->
	
		<script type='text/javascript'>
		
	
		var myVar;
		var prevUrl = "";
		$(document).ready(function(){	
			var url=document.location.href;
			if(url.split("/").length>=3)
			{
				var siteUrl=url.split("/")[3];
				if(siteUrl.toLowerCase()=='pages')
				{
					$("a.rmRootLink:first").css({"font-weight":"bold"});
				}
				else
				{
					$("a.rmRootLink[href*='"+siteUrl+"']").css({"font-weight":"bold"});
				}
			}
			else
			{
				$("a.rmRootLink:first").css({"font-weight":"bold"});
			}

			
			//For Touch Menu Hover
			
			
			$("a").bind('touchstart', function() 
			{
			    $("a.rmLink").click(function(event)
    			{
					if (navigator.userAgent.match(/Android/i))
					{
						if(!($(this).hasClass("hover")))
						{
							$("a").removeClass("hover");
							$(this).addClass("hover");
							event.preventDefault();
							var url = $(this).attr('href');
							if (url == prevUrl)
								window.location.href=url;
							else
								prevUrl = url;
						}
					}
				});
			
					  $("a.static").click(function(event)
						{
							if(!($(this).hasClass("hover")))
									{
										$("a").removeClass("hover");
										$(this).addClass("hover");
										event.preventDefault();
										
									}
						});
					});

			
			// Table
			try
			{
				toggle2('contentDisplay01', 'contentHeader01','0','true','ctl00_m_g_a5216398_6a54_4ec1_9dc2_4f57c0a56ef9_ctl00');
				
			}
			catch(err)
			{
				var funStatus = err;
				
			}
						
			
			//For Chrome Broswer Hover Event Start
			
			//==========span.additional-background======================================================
				var myVar;
				
				var isChrome = (/Chrome/.test(navigator.userAgent) && /Google Inc/.test(navigator.vendor));
				if(isChrome)
				{
				
				$("span.additional-background").hover(function()
					{
						
							clearTimeout(myVar);
							//Hover Focus In
							if(($(this).parent().parent().hasClass("static")))
							{
								if(!($(this).parent().parent().hasClass("hover")))
								{
									$("li.static").removeClass("hover");
									//$('#foo').removeAttr('style');
									$("ul.dynamic").attr('style', '');
									
									$(this).parent().parent().addClass("hover");
									
								}
							}
							else if(($(this).parent().parent().hasClass("dynamic")))
							{
								if(!($(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().hasClass("hover")))
								{
									$("li.static").removeClass("hover");
									$("ul.dynamic").attr('style', '');
									
									$(this).parent().parent().parent().parent().addClass("hover");							
								}
							}				
						
					},function()
								{ 	
									//Hover Focus Out
									
										myVar=setTimeout(function(){$("li.static").removeClass("hover");$("ul.dynamic").attr('style', '');},1000);
									
									
								}
							  	);		
		
				}					
					
			
				//===================================================================
				
				
			//For Chrome Browser Hover Event End
		
			});
		
		</script>
